## Open-source contributions
Besides my own projects, I have also issued small contributions to noteworthy open-source projects: 
- A bug fix in [Cypress](https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress/pull/720)
- A localization and documentation improvement in AirBnB’s [react-dates](https://github.com/react-dates/react-dates/pull/1171)
- An accessibility improvement in [Ant Design](https://github.com/ant-design/ant-design/pull/57695)
- An accessibility improvement in [Next.js](https://github.com/vercel/next.js/pull/31147)
- An accessibility improvement in [Slate](https://github.com/ianstormtaylor/slate/pull/5100)
- Multiple accessibility improvements in [Sanity](https://github.com/sanity-io/sanity/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3Akittygiraudel+is%3Aclosed)
- Multiple documentation and tooling improvements in [Fela](https://github.com/robinweser/fela/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3Akittygiraudel+is%3Aclosed)
- Some minor enhancements in [Knip](https://github.com/webpro-nl/knip/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3Akittygiraudel+is%3Aclosed)
- … and [more](https://github.com/search?q=author%3Akittygiraudel+++++&type=pullrequests&query=author%3Akittygiraudel+is%3Apr&state=closed).
